Since there are only two keywordºáSPAN CONTROL 145ºÅ65ºÖ1ºÜ65ºäLºà65ºéºàparameters listed, the third parameter is assumed to beºçSPAN CONTROL 145ºÅ67ºÖ1ºÜ67ºäLºà67ºéºàpositional.  Positional parameters always preceed keywordºãSPAN CONTROL 145ºÅ69ºÖ1ºÜ69ºäLºà69ºéºàparameters in SAS macro definitions, so the first parameterºâSPAN CONTROL 145ºÅ68ºÖ1ºÜ68ºäLºà68ºéºàa positional parameter, which is given the values of firstºäSPAN CONTROL 145ºÅ71ºÖ1ºÜ71ºäLºà71ºéºàmacro array "aa".
